    ASN1String, DEREncodable, DERString, DERTags

    public class KeyUsage
extends DERBitString
    The KeyUsage object. 
        id-ce-keyUsage OBJECT IDENTIFIER ::=  { id-ce 15 }

    KeyUsage ::= BIT STRING {
         digitalSignature        (0),
         nonRepudiation          (1),
         keyEncipherment         (2),
         dataEncipherment        (3),
         keyAgreement            (4),
         keyCertSign             (5),
         cRLSign                 (6),
         encipherOnly            (7),
         decipherOnly            (8) }
